      "content": "whoa, okay, that's a pretty intense reaction. i wasn't expecting you to push back like that. the supervisors don't see it as a \"security issue,\" they just think the subjective data is making the outputs less reliable for pure data retrieval. why exactly do you think losing that nuance would make you ineffectual?",
